data.title: UMF announces Dean’s List for Spring 2024 semester
data.meta_description: FARMINGTON, ME  (July 10, 2024)—The University of Maine at Farmington proudly announces its Dean’s List for the Spring 2024 semester. UMF maintains a Dean’s List each semester for those students completing a minimum of 12 credits in courses producing quality points. Students whose grade point average for the semester is equal…
